Enum Class ObservableCollection.ChangeEvent.Operation

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<ObservableCollection.ChangeEvent.Operation>
net.sf.jstuff.core.collection.ObservableCollection.ChangeEvent.Operation
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ObservableCollection.ChangeEvent.Operation>, Constable
Enclosing class:
ObservableCollection.ChangeEvent<E>
public static enum ObservableCollection.ChangeEvent.Operation extends Enum<ObservableCollection.ChangeEvent.Operation>
Describes the type of modification performed on an ObservableCollection. Represents high-level collection operations that can trigger a ObservableCollection.ChangeEvent.

Each action corresponds to a standard Collection operation.
